      teach thee."That which the soul unaided cannot know, the Master will teach. That is 
      to say, presumably: This Power or Presence is a link between your own 
      "body" or atmosphere and the realities of Great Things.As soon as the sphere-"body" (the psychic envelope of normal man is 
