      brought into such perfect relationship as to become one. Then the little 
      soul would become a Great Soul or Master, a Perfect or Balanced Soul.The concluding sentences are evidently drawn from two different 
      traditions of the original text; they are two separatepg 72endings copied down one after the other. It is thus to be conjectured 
      that there were several variants of this ritual, and that it was, 
      therefore, widely known and used in Gnostic circles.It must, however, have been at first kept very secret, for later on in 
